# FluxA AI Wallet MCP Environment Variables

# Data directory (optional)
# FLUXA_DATA_DIR=/custom/path/to/data

# ==================================================
# Agent ID Configuration - Choose ONE method below:
# ==================================================

# Method 1: Use existing Agent ID credentials (highest priority)
# If you already have registered and have these credentials, use this method
# AGENT_ID=your-agent-id-uuid
# AGENT_TOKEN=your-agent-token
# AGENT_JWT=your-jwt-token

# Method 2: Provide registration information
# Use this if you don't have credentials yet
# When configured, calling init_agent_id with {} will auto-register
# AGENT_EMAIL=user@example.com
# AGENT_NAME=Claude Desktop - John's MacBook
# CLIENT_INFO=Claude Desktop v1.0 on macOS 14.1

# ==================================================
# API Endpoints (optional, for testing)
# ==================================================

# AGENT_ID_API=https://agentid.fluxapay.xyz
# WALLET_API=https://walletapi.fluxapay.xyz
